<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1743453.Gospo_ica"><img alt="Gospođica" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1452219649l/1743453._SY75_.jpg" />
